Individuals can download the app through Google Play Store and they can choose their first mission to start contributing processing capacity and make progress on the game.

Alantu was founded in 2014 by Carlos De Venezia, Ignacio Olaciregui, Victor Calvello, and Matias Mediña Andregnette.
